    public static class QueryResult.SingletonQueryResult<V>
extends QueryResult.EmptyQueryResult<V>
    An implementation of QueryResult interface that wraps a single value.

    This implementation cannot be closed, ie calls to close() do nothing and calls to isClosed() always return false.
